Build Instructions
==================
* Place smpp.jar in lib/  <https://github.com/cornet/logica-smpp>
$ ant


Running the Simulator
=====================
$ cd build/jar
$ java -cp smscsim.jar:../../lib/smpp.jar com.logica.smscsim.Simulator

* Hit `1` to start he simulator
* Enter a port number
* See users.txt for user/pass

